(29, 0, 'Social Media Marketing for Businesses', '<h2 style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 24px; color: #0a3498; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Social Media Marketing for Businesses</h2>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 25px 0px 0px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: #414141; color: #0a3498; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 20px; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">About the Seminar</h3>\r\n<h4 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Objectives</h4>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">At the end of the program, the participants should be able to:<br /><br /> Understand the secrets and strengths of social media marketing in the Philippines<br /> Utilize social media marketing opportunities to reach new potential market and to create brand awareness<br /> Understand further the social media marketing strategy<br /> Harness and understand the anatomy of the most relevant social media marketing tools today<br /> Find potential new product or business<br /> Create a personal development plan</p>\r\n<h4 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Who Should Participate</h4>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;"> Business owners<br /> Marketing managers and staffs<br /> Sales professionals<br /> Those who are interested in using the social media in promoting products or services</p>\r\n<h4 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Key Topics</h4>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">1. What social media marketing can do for your business<br /><br />2. Best practices in the Philippines  success stories<br /><br />3. Social media ROI and metrics  