(30, 0, 'Internet Marketing Seminar', '<h2 style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; font-size: 24px; color: #0a3498; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Internet Marketing Seminar</h2>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 25px 0px 0px; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: #414141; color: #0a3498; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 20px; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">About the Seminar</h3>\r\n<h4 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Overview</h4>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">Selling online provides the greatest amount of potential income. It is practical and cost-effective. It can be done by students, housewives, and almost anybody.</p>\r\n<h4 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Objective</h4>\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-left: 15px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">\r\n<li>The seminar aims to teach the attendees how to earn via the Internet. Specifically, it teaches how to sell products online, and make your company visible on the Web.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Who Should Participate</h4>\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-left: 15px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">\r\n<li>students</li>\r\n<li>businessmen who want to market their products online</li>\r\n<li>those seeking a home-based business</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; line-height: normal;">Key Topics</h4>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; color: #343434; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">1. Introduction<br />a. Internet Population in the Philippines<br />b. Success Stories  Online Businesses<br