(69, 0, 'Data Analytics: the Newbies'' Guide to Advancing Their Careers', '<header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/data-analytics-the-newbies-guide-to-advancing-their-careers-tickets-19332459908?aff=ebrowse#listing-organizer" data-d-duration="1500" data-d-offset="0" data-d-destination="#listing-organizer" data-xd-wired="scroll-to">By: Parsimony Inc.</a>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Event Description</h2>\r\n<div data-xd-wired="read-more">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Whether you''re a Graduating Student, a Career Shiftee or a Beginner preparing to become aData Analyst, this course is for YOU. Get ahead of everyone and realize that the difference between you and the experienced others is just a training away. Learn how to look at the data of companies (depending on which type of data) and create insightful reports. Also, get to meet our experienced trainers and consult on how you can advance your career in data analytics -- for FREE. <br /><br />Data Analytics or Data Science is one of the most sought out services nowadays here in the Philippines. Grab this chance to know what the Philippines is doing in the Analytics space and how we can respond in this new trend.</p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Benefits</p>\r\n<p>The participants will gain the following and a whole lot more:</p>\r\n<p>1. Understand the different types of data and get to work with real data</p>\r\n<p>2. Know how to give meaningful insights and IMPRESS your Managers in the company</p>\r\n<p>3. Learn different tools and methods for analyzing data</p>\r\n<p>4. Own your career by learning the path to success in the Data Analytics track!<br /><br /><br />Course Outline</p>\r\n<p>This training is part of Parsimony Inc.sEnterprise Data Analytics Programaimed at shaping the individuals in their knowledge and application of Data Analytics.<br /><br />Below is the outline for this course:<br /><br />1. Introduction<br 