(71, 0, 'Freelancing 101: Creating a sustainable career and freelance lifestyle', '<header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/success-workshop-freelancing-101-creating-a-sustainable-career-and-freelance-lifestyle-tickets-19240628237?aff=ebrowse#listing-organizer" data-d-duration="1500" data-d-offset="0" data-d-destination="#listing-organizer" data-xd-wired="scroll-to">By: AED GLOBAL</a>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Event Description</h2>\r\n<div data-xd-wired="read-more">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Philippines has been one of the top countries in the world that has a huge freelancer base. However, freelancers are having problems in terms of defining their work roles and habits. The entire workshop will include classes covering basic freelancer ethics and advanced strategies in building your freelancer career.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>WORKSHOP COVERAGE:</h2>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><img src="https://c2.staticflickr.com/4/3502/3946614647_fc3fbb9f77.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>MODULE 1: What is freelancing?</p>\r\n<p>Learn what freelancing really is. Determine how to present yourself professionally in an online environement. What are the do''s and don''ts in communication online? How do you approach employers and how do you stand out?</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5581/14929512628_138679d966.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>MODULE 2: Online Visibility and Interview Protocols</p>\r\n<p>In a virtual workspace, you will not have the change to meet the employers in person, so dressing up and wearing your best black shoes would not work. Freelancing has a different code in terms of gaining that impactful first impression.</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://c1.staticflickr.com/7/6144/6021688217_5f1faa3c82.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>MODULE 3: Communication and Reputation</p>\r\n<p>Freelancing is a very challenging profession. It will be your most rewarding work experience if you are following certain codes of conduct, but others fail because they do not know how to properly communicate in this type of environment.</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://s.evbuc.com/https_proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2Flh6.ggpht.com%2FGriwt9Yk05buaFcVegBYZAYU22arqt56FjJl7sKqfqL6AB-ap2BKErwSeNr1QcTD2-m7nLsv3nJalCiu%3Ds620&amp;sig=ADR2i79saIqKuatvj4G23DsXuJl0op_Fyw" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>MODULE 4: Creating a Lasting Freelancing Career</p>\r\n<p>This is the part of the workshop where we will tackle how to divert your "part-time" freelance job into a lasting career. We are also discussing the ways you can properly file your taxes and get government benefits while working at home.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>FAQs</h2>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Are there ID requirements or an age limit to enter the event?</p>\r\n<p>You have to be at least 18 years old to attend the event.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Is my registration/ticket transferrable?</p>\r\n<p>The registration ticket is non-transferrable.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Can I update my registration information?</p>\r\n<p>You can update your contact information by updating your EventBrite account and sending us an email regarding the change.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Do I have to bring my printed ticket to the event?</p>\r\n<p>Yes. We have a no ticket, no entry policy.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>What is the refund policy?</p>\r\n<p>There is no refund in the tickets once you have purchased them. The workshops offer limited slots to anyone who would like to join, so reserving your slot is a full commitment.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>The name on the registration/ticket doesn''t match the attendee. Is that okay?</p>\r\n<p>No. Please make sure that the details on your event sign up is the same as yourFULL NAME.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>I am interested in Sponsoring the event. How do I get in?<br />Please contact us to get a quote on the Sponsorship fee.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<dl>\r\n<dt data-automation="listing-info-language">WHEN</dt>\r\n<dd><time data-automation="event-