(72, 0, 'MON, DEC 14, 2015 AT 8:00 AM Succeed with Quality: Introduction to Quality Management - Cebu', '<header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/succeed-with-quality-introduction-to-quality-management-cebu-tickets-19470768593?aff=ebrowse#listing-organizer" data-d-duration="1500" data-d-offset="0" data-d-destination="#listing-organizer" data-xd-wired="scroll-to">By: Parsimony Inc.</a>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Event Description</h2>\r\n<div data-xd-wired="read-more">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Qualityis an indispensable key to any companys global competitiveness. Likewise,RETAINING and REPEATING customers are achieved by avoiding poor quality services/outputs. Large and small companies implement Quality Management to increase customer satisfaction and improve performance.<br /><br />This training introduces the principles, skills and tools needed to establish Quality Management system in various business sectors and organizations such as Information Technology, Manufacturing, Healthcare, Education, etc.<br /><br />Team Leaders, Managers or Supervisors must learn how to efficiently utilize resources to achieve the common goal of their organization while maintaining quality of deliverables.Learn how to implement Quality Management to your team and be aware of the LATEST trends in IT/BPO Quality space. Hear from a Senior Quality Practice Leader who has implemented successful Quality Management principles and methodologies for almost 20 years in different industries both local and international.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Benefits</p>\r\n<p>The participants will gain the following and a whole lot more:</p>\r\n<p>1. Knowledge on how to benchmark with the industrys quality state;</p>\r\n<p>2. Understand the concepts of quality management process and process control; and</p>\r\n<p>3. Explore the commonly used tools and techniques for process improvement</p>\r\n<p><br /><br />Course Outline</p>\r\n<p>This training is part of Parsimony Inc.sQuality ExcellenceProgramaimed at shaping the individuals in their knowledge and application of Basic Project Management.<br /><br />Below is the outline for this course:<br /><br />1. Introduction<br />2. Building your Organization''s Quality Roadmap<br />3. Quality Framework<br />4. Quality Tools<br />5. The Quality Journey</p>\r\n<p>Plus, get the chance to consult your Quality Management concerns. Professional Trainer''s details are available upon request.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Registration Fee</p>\r\n<p>P4,000  Regular Rate</p>\r\n<p>P3,500  Early Bird Rate (1 week before the training)</p>\r\n<p>P3,000.00  per pax for groups with a minimum of 5 members</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Inclusions: Certificate of Completion<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Other Trainings in CEBU</p>\r\n<p>Analytics for Business Success - Dec. 15, 2015<br />Ensuring Success with Effective Project Management - Dec. 16, 2015<br />Lean Six Sigma Essentials - Jan. 21, 2016</p>\r\n<p><br />Contact Us to Register</p>\r\n<p title="Page 1">REGISTER HERE:<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/18WeAQ6LXunlRLHJ2bdhjLv7sD8SzN0XsyqQLTDQ5c5E/viewform" rel="nofollow">Parsimony Inc. Registration Form</a><br /><br />Website:<a href="http://www.parsimony-inc.com/" rel="nofollow">www.parsimony-inc.com</a><br />Email:parsimony@parsimony-inc.com<br />Landline: (+02) 274 9802<br />Mobile: (+63) 917 987 6669 |(+63) 926 670 6569</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<dl>\r\n<dt data-automation="listing-info-language">WHEN</dt>\r\n<dd><time data-automation="event-details-time">Monday, December 14, 2015 from 8:00 AM to 12:00 PM (PHT)-<a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/succeed-with-quality-introduction-to-quality-management-cebu-tickets-19470768593?aff=ebrowse#add-to-calendar-modal" data-automation="add-to-calendar" data-xd-wired="modal">Add to Calendar</a></time></dd>\r\n<dt>WHERE</dt>\r\n<dd>Best Western Hotel - Cebu, Cebu PH -<a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/succee