(73, 0, 'Add Overseas Customers without leaving the Philippines (evening session)', '<h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; color: #404040; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2em; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Making your thrivingonline business more successful by introducing it to North American customers and partners</h2>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">The success of manyonline business ownersand multi-level marketing distributors in the Philippines, has played an important role in making the country one of the top 40 economies in the world. </p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Our Go-Global conference seeks to empower and coachFilipino entrepreneurs so they can introduce their online business to North Americans andcompete successfully for their purchasingdollars.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Many leave the Philippines in search of a better life in the United States and Canadabecause of the strength of their currencies and employment prospects despite sometimes very harsh weather conditions and alarming crime rate.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">This conference will leave you with a plan to earn money in North America while enjoying the benefits of living in the Philippines.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">"The Republic of the Philippinesis the best example of successful multi-level marketing in Asia in recent years.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">I want to help Filipino independent distributors to attain a new level of income by accessing the North American market with their product and services. I have a business development program that will increase your customer base and your downline of associate distributors. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">I will share this effective strategy with you and commit to helping the first 300 MLM/Online Philippinesbusinesses launch withinNorth America in the first month of the new year. You will see results in your first month."</span><br /><br /><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">R C Hunter<br /></span>Chief Executive Officer<br />Go-Global Int''l, Donation-In-A-Box</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';"></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; color: #72858c; background: transparent;"></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">"In our fast paced technological culture, we have overlooked some simple and timeless principles.</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">These principles are necessary and still relevant.</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">"Do unto others as you would like them to do unto you" is still the golden rule.</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">We believe in equipping individuals with the tools needed for success.</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">Etiquette gives you a professional, poised and polished edge in any social or business environment.</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">It is perfect for anyone; children, teens, college students, adults and professionals.</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''arial black'', ''avant garde'';">Our goal is to help further develop and refine the interpersonal skills needed to navigate the rapidly changing world."<br /><br />Christine Carmichael<br /></span>Executive Director<br />Flemming Academy of Etiquette</p>', 300, 'Add_Overseas_Customers_without_leaving_the_Philippines__evening_session_', 1, 1, 1449548995, 0, 0, 0, 11, 'main', 0, 0, 'Add_Overseas_Customers_without_leaving_the_Philippines__evening_session_', '0.000', 'and,you,business,north,online,your,their,will', 'kg', 1449571214, 'making your thrivingonline business more successful by introducing it to north american customers and partners\r\nthe success of manyonline business ownersand multi-level marketing distributors in the philippines, has played an important role in maki', 'm', '0.000', '0.000', '0.000', 0, 'all', '', 0, 0, 0, 1449571138, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 'Add Overseas Customers without leaving the Philippines (evening session)', 'add-overseas-customers-without-leaving-the-philippines-evening-session', '0.0000000', '0.0000000', '', 0, '');
