(76, 0, 'Project Management Fundamentals - Manila', '<header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/project-management-fundamentals-manila-tickets-19680134813?aff=ebrowse#listing-organizer" data-d-duration="1500" data-d-offset="0" data-d-destination="#listing-organizer" data-xd-wired="scroll-to">By: Parsimony Inc.</a>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Event Description</h2>\r\n<div data-xd-wired="read-more">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Project Managementis the application of processes, methods, knowledge, skills and experience to achieve the project objectives.</p>\r\n<p>The concepts taught in this course can be used as part of a comprehensive end-to-end program or as standalone techniques and tools in your respective activities and operations.This course will also give a thorough overview of each of the Knowledge Areas in Project Management. Participants will be able to learn the right skills and know the right tools/templates to implement for an effective project management.</p>\r\n<p>This training will help you not just complete projects end-to-end but to manage future projects in sustainable ways that empower the stakeholders below and above your organization.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Benefits</p>\r\n<p>In this training conducted by Parsimony Inc., anyone who intend to manage a project will gain the following:</p>\r\n<p>1. Essential information to prepare and complete your projects;</p>\r\n<p>2. Increased competency and skills in Project Management; and</p>\r\n<p>3. Discover critical concepts for you to plan, implement, control and close any types of projects</p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><br /><br />Upcoming Trainings<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p title="Page 2">Succeed with Quality: Introduction to Quality Management<br />Jan. 30, 2015<br /><br />Advanced Project Management<br />Feb. 27, 2015<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Payment Inclusion<br />- Food: For whole day trainings, weinclude lunch &amp