(89, 0, 'CLEAN BANDIT: LIVE IN MANILA', '<p>English electronic pop group Clean Bandit will be making their Manila concert debut to be held at Valkyrie Nightclub in The Palace Manila on December 2015. They''re the band behind the 2014 hit single, "Rather Be", a collaboration with Jess Glynne. Concert details as follows.<br /><a name="more"></a></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div><strong>December 10, 2015 - 8:00pm</strong></div>\r\n<div>Valkyrie Nightclub, The Palace, Uptown Bonifacio, Taguig City<br />18+ event</div>\r\n<div><strong></strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>TICKET PRICE</strong></div>\r\n<div>General Admission - P2,650</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tickets are available at SM Tickets outlets nationwide and online: www.smtickets.com. Call 470.2222 for ticket inquiries.</div>\r\n<div>For table reservations, contact The Palace Pool Club: 0917.689.8888</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>', 4321, 'CLEAN_BANDIT__LIVE_IN_MANILA', 1, 1, 1449550855, 0, 0, 0, 11, 'main', 0, 0, 'CLEAN_BANDIT__LIVE_IN_MANILA', '0.000', 'palace,ticket,valkyrie,nightclub,concert,manila,december,for', 'kg', 1449572348, 'english electronic pop group clean bandit will be making their manila concert debut to be held at valkyrie nightclub in the palace manila on december 2015. they''re the band behind the 2014 hit single, "rather be", a collaboration with jess glynne. concer', 'm', '0.000', '0.000', '0.000', 0, 'all', '', 0, 0, 0, 1449572273, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, 'CLEAN BANDIT: LIVE IN MANILA', 'clean-bandit-live-in-manila', '0.0000000', '0.0000000', '', 0, ''),
