(109, 106, '', '<h3 class="post-title entry-title" style="margin: 0.75em 0px 0px; position: relative; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: Merriweather; color: #ffffff; background-color: #000000;">God Gave Me You Tour: Bryan White Live in Manila</h3>\r\n<div class="post-header" style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; font-size: 12.6px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; background-color: #000000;"></div>\r\n<div id="post-body-1744033372738500376" class="post-body entry-content" style="width: 610px; font-size: 15.4px; line-height: 1.4; position: relative; color: #ffffff; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; background-color: #000000;">\r\n<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a style="color: #aa9bb5; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;" href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VPUgYPGAA5A/VgjZUG9ScQI/AAAAAAAATTA/c4WimUbYX4U/s1600/Bryan%2BWhite%2Bphoto.jpg"><img style="border: 1px solid #a3a3a3; position: relative; padding: 5px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0980392) 1px 1px 5px; background: #999999;" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VPUgYPGAA5A/VgjZUG9ScQI/AAAAAAAATTA/c4WimUbYX4U/s320/Bryan%2BWhite%2Bphoto.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="255" border="0" /></a></div>\r\n<span style="font-size: 15.4px; line-height: 32.3724px;">Country pop superstar Bryan White, will perform here in Manila for the first time as he brings the God Gave Me You Tour on December 2015 at the Araneta Coliseum. He''s been known as the singer of the hit single today, "God Gave Me You". Concert details as follows.</span><br style="font-size: 15.4px; line-height: 32.3724px;" /><a style="font-size: 15.4px; line-height: 32.3724px;" name="more"></a><br style="font-size: 15.4px; line-height: 32.3724px;" />\r\n<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a style="color: #aa9bb5; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;" href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QPLUoMe-bQw/