(110, 0, '2016 Rainbow Serpent Festival', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px;"><img style="border: 0px;" src="https://cdn.evbuc.com/eventlogos/107601453/pagesgen5.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="277" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px;">Rainbow Serpent Festival has come a long way since it started. From a small gathering in a secluded clearing, to an internationally recongnised, multifaceted weekend of dance, colour, expression and celebration.</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px;">People now travel from all over the world to Western Victoria to experience what some have said is the best outdoor festival of its type in the Southern Hemisp</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px;">here.<br /><br />No longer just an electronic music festival these days you can expect to experience a unique combination of music, art, performance, spiritual education, relaxation and healing.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; tex