a Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;"><a style="color: #00b7ff;" href="http://www.rainbowserpent.net/2016-festival-tickets" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px;"><img style="border: 0px;" src="https://cdn.evbuc.com/eventlogos/107601453/ticketfaqs.png" alt="" /></span></a></p>', 5000, '2016_Rainbow_Serpent_Festival', 1, 1, 1449573144, 0, 0, 0, 11, 'main', 0, 0, '2016_Rainbow_Serpent_Festival', '0.000', 'and,festival,dance,have,our,ticket,you,experience', 'kg', 1449573576, 'rainbow serpent festival has come a long way since it started. from a small gathering in a secluded clearing, to an internationally recongnised, multifaceted weekend of dance, colour, expression and celebration.people now travel from all over the wor', 'm', '0.000', '0.000', '0.000', 0, 'all', '', 0, 0, 0, 1449573253, 0, 0, '', 0, 0, '2016 Rainbow Serpent Festival', '2016-rainbow-serpent-festival', '0.0000000', '0.0000000', '', 0, '');
