(168, 0, 'Native RTL Support', '', '<p><a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=85&amp;Itemid=488"><img class="article-thumb image-border" src="http://demo.joomlashine.com/joomla-templates/jsn_metro/free/images/touliver.jpg" border="0" alt="" /></a>Native RTL support means that every elements on the page is mirror swapped including layout, menus, typography, icons...everything. All JoomlaShine templates are equipped with native RTL layout support. We spent huge amount of time tweaking every tiny details of the template to make it look absolutely awesome in RTL mode. Everything is horizontally-flipped including dropdown main menu and side menu.</p>\n<p><a class="link-button button-light" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=85&amp;Itemid=488">Read more</a></p>', 1, 'mainbody-bottom', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"jsn-icon-display","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
