 ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px;">People now travel from all over the world to Western Victoria to experience what some have said is the best outdoor festival of its type in the Southern Hemisp</span><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px;">here.<br /><br />No longer just an electronic music festival these days you can expect to experience a unique combination of music, art, performance, spiritual education, relaxation and healing.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino; font-size: medium; color: #999999; line-height: 24px;"><em>"While dancing their Dreamings, aborigines spiritually connect themselves to the land and to the Dreamtime. The drumming of feet during the dance draws the earth into dialogue with the dancers, allowing the ceremony to bring the power of the Dreaming to life."</em></span><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px;"><img style="border: 0px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://cdn.evbuc.com/eventlogos/107601453/line.jpg" alt="" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 8px; line-height: normal; color: #666666; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: #333333; font-fa